{"tid":2053004,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"會見英國代表 蔡英文：期待英國與台灣一起撐香港人","createTime":"2020-06-06T02:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T05:15:40.000Z","uid":144372,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"39a5f62bbe8a514bfdbf1c506d2d03c64b7ac019","tid":2053004,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:55:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/article/2729044\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F2729044&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=b64e1ce9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/article/2729044</a><br />\n<br />\n英國在台辦事處代表唐凱琳（Catherine Nettleton）5日上午到總統府，先後拜會總統蔡英文及副總統賴清德。針對香港議題，蔡英文也對唐凱琳表示，民主、自由、人權都是台英共享的價值，台灣期待能與英國共同努力，相挺香港人民，相挺普世價值，一起為世界做出更多的貢獻。<br />\n蔡英文說明，台灣和英國是理念相近的夥伴，對於「香港版國安法」立法決議的通過，台安看到英國拉布（Dominic Raab）外相與美國國務卿、加拿大及澳洲外長，共同發表聯合聲明表達關切。英國正在研議因應作為，台灣也啟動了專案，將進一步協助香港朋友。"},{"pid":"eb869b1aecf3519965985c68379ccaa63ade609a","tid":2053004,"uid":155107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:56:42.000Z","msg":"小英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34023add4b9105fe5644f3ac24a84b0a036b314c","tid":2053004,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:59:18.000Z","msg":"睇下五毛幾驚台港聯手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35ttSAT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35ttSAT.png&h=c6d3cf5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5bcf5e4b0b81889e04401fe08c6b3cf59a142719","tid":2053004,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T03:00:47.000Z","msg":"翻譯: 期待英國及台灣一齊屌鳩中國"},{"pid":"50e48e4ae50c8728be10a08f20c1189ea2430ab0","tid":2053004,"uid":113183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T03:13:21.000Z","msg":"<im